Description :
        What should a woman do in ancient times? Falling in love or having a beautiful boy? NONO! Of course, I've to make a fortune by using modern knowledge to do business! What about beauty, fitness, and swimming business in ancient? How about mahjong? Do you want children's educational toys? A modern woman has time-traveled to ancient times and tricked the emperor into playing with the prince. All her childhood sweethearts and lovers, all can't compare to the career in her eyes! Want to pursue her?
